    "content": {
        "data": "{\"textPanel\":{\"list\":[{\"title\":\"目的\",\"data\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">通过实验观察，了解认识气体的自发扩散过程。</span></span></span></p>\\n\"},{\"title\":\"原理\",\"data\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\">不需要外界的任何作用，气体通过分子的扩散自发地混合均匀。</span></span></p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\">HCl+NH<sub>3</sub>=NH<sub>4</sub>Cl</span></span></p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\">H<sub>2</sub>+F<sub>2</sub>=2HF</span></span></p>\\n\"},{\"title\":\"用品\",\"data\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">药品：收集满氨气、氯化氢、氯气、氢气、氟气的集气瓶，玻璃片</span></span></span></p>\\n\"},{\"title\":\"步骤\",\"data\":\"<ol>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">将装有氨气的广口瓶扣在装有氯化氢的广口瓶上，抽掉玻璃片，观察现象。</span></span></span></li>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">将装有氢气的广口瓶扣在装有氯气的广口瓶上，抽掉玻璃片，观察现象。</span></span></span></li>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">将装有氢气的广口瓶扣在装有氟气的广口瓶上，抽掉玻璃片，观察现象。</span></span></span></li>\\n</ol>\\n\"},{\"title\":\"现象\",\"data\":\"<ol>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">两瓶中均产生白烟。</span></span></span></li>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:26px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:等线\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black\\\">氢气瓶中颜色逐渐加深，氯气瓶中颜色逐渐变浅，最终两瓶中颜色相同。</span></span></span></li>\\n\\t<li style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">剧烈反应，发生爆炸。</li>\\n</ol>\\n\"}],\"x\":420,\"y\":110,\"width\":600,\"height\":565},\"chemData\":{\"chemBackGroundColor\":3422529,\"viewStack\":{\"x\":-2407.32209179681,\"y\":-161.8044870799501,\"scaleX\":1.2230676050966458,\"scaleY\":1.2230676050966458},\"magnifierData\":[],\"microAniData\":{},\"children\":[{\"breakImgAlpha\":0,\"nbSolidGraPos\":null,\"pharaohSerpentData\":null,\"x\":2203.063,\"y\":708.438,\"rotation\":0,\"index\":0,\"name\":\"H2\",\"uuid\":\"2879485279018039\",\"addedNode\":[\"9768197552768918\"],\"currentPlugCurValue\":null,\"currentArea\":null,\"plugAnimation\":false,\"fun\":false,\"holdAnimation\":false,\"scaleX\":1,\"scaleY\":1,\"areaWasFullAry\":[],\"constructorAttribute\":{\"dataBuild\":true},\"medicineData\":{\"liquid\":[],\"solid\":{},\"gas\":[{\"dat\":{\"chemical\":\"H2\"},\"mol\":0.010219079722275821,\"temp\":25}],\"temp\":25,\"ion\":[],\"dissolve\":[],\"ionMedicine\":[]},\"bringToFront\":true,\"instanceName\":\"main.gas.H2^2\",\"pivotX\":0,\"dataVersion\":8,\"plugAnimationOpen\":true,\"openArea\":0,\"isCoverGS\":true,\"labelHide\":false,\"coveredGasBottle\":\"9768197552768918\",\"children\":[{\"breakImgAlpha\":0,\"nbSolidGraPos\":null,\"pharaohSerpentData\":null,\"x\":223,\"y\":0,\"rotation\":3.141592653589793,\"index\":0,\"name\":\"F2\",\"uuid\":\"9768197552768918\",\"addedNode\":[\"2879485279018039\"],\"currentPlugCurValue\":null,\"currentArea\":null,\"plugAnimation\":false,\"fun\":false,\"holdAnimation\":false,\"scaleX\":1,\"scaleY\":1,\"areaWasFullAry\":[],\"constructorAttribute\":{\"dataBuild\":true},\"medicineData\":{\"liquid\":[],\"solid\":{},\"gas\":[{\"dat\":{\"chemical\":\"F2\"},\"mol\":0.010204547363301768,\"temp\":25},{\"dat\":{\"chemical\":\"O2\"},\"mol\":0.000002906471794810172,\"temp\":25},{\"dat\":{\"chemical\":\"N2\"},\"mol\":0.000011625887179240689,\"temp\":25}],\"temp\":25,\"ion\":[],\"dissolve\":[],\